    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Pale Maw operatives are the elite strike teams of the Entropy cult — fanatics trained in both martial and psychological warfare. Robed in purple and silver vestments of entropy, they move with coordinated purpose, using Heretic's Mark to designate targets for their companions to finish. Their Unshakeable Faith makes them immune to fear and mental manipulation. Operatives appear where the Pale Maw needs precise, controlled violence rather than overwhelming force.</p>",
